    "uen": "200922661N",
    "description": "<p>LIKE Building Materials (S) Pte Ltd has vast experience in many types of metal works projects in Singapore. We have 4 factories in China forming a whole line of raw material processing, including cutting, bending, v cutting, powder coating, plating, etc, all under one roof.</p>\n\n<p>Our main fabricating arm in China Foshan Nanhai LIKE Building Material Co., Ltd. is located in Nanhai Lishui, specializing in the production of aluminium alloy honeycomb panels, indoor and outdoor metal wall panels, metal ceiling; a modern metal building materials manufacturing enterprise with the comprehensive integration of design, production, marketing and installation. From design to products testing, installation and construction services, the company is in strict accordance with GB/T19001-2008 idt ISO9001：2008 quality assurance system of strict control and management. <br />\n<br />\nWith an area of 14,500 square meters, we have three factories that are aluminium panel plant, steel structure workshop and spraying process shop in China. All production and management are conducted by 18 department. <br />\n<br />\nOur company is well-known for its aluminium alloy honeycomb panels, metal curtain walls (aluminium board), metal ceiling (metal ceiling board) and the manufacturer of accessory products. Lots of foreign companies in Singapore, Germany, French, Italy and also domestic ones have been established closely cooperative relationships with our company working on products research and development, producing process and sales of aluminum-magnesium alloy construction projects, metal ceiling and other accessory products. LIKE has strong technical strength, well-established and skilled teams in the field of production, installation and sales, been enjoying a high reputation among the peer community. </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n",
